Privacy Policy
Last Updated: August 2, 2025
This Privacy Policy describes how Bolta ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, stores, and shares your personal information when you interact with our services ("Services"), including:

Visiting our website: https://bolta-12e5a.web.app
Using our mobile application (Bolta)
Exchanging earned coins for discounts at health-related businesses
Participating in related sales, marketing, or events
If you have questions or concerns, contact us at lnarsia12@gmail.com.
Summary of Key Points
What personal information do we process? We collect information like your name, email, and app activity.
Do we process sensitive information? No.
Do we collect third-party data? No.
Why do we process your data? To operate and improve our Services, ensure security, and comply with legal obligations.
Do we share your data? Only with business partners or during business transitions like mergers.
What rights do you have? Depending on your location, you may access, correct, or delete your data.
How can you exercise those rights? Contact us or submit a data subject access request.
